longBusinessSummary: Ceylon Graphite Corp. engages in the exploration and production of graphite mines in Sri Lanka. The company holds a land package of approximately 120 square kilometers grids containing vein graphite deposits. Ceylon Graphite Corp. is based in Vancouver, Canada.
